[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ひあああああ！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01066",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "今のは……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01067",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "行ってみましょう。タイニーたちもいるかもしれない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01068",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "いた……！　って、どういう状況？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01069",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "や、やめてくれ！　悪かった！　もうしねえ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01070",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "賞金首の「ヌルスラの鷹」もこれで一巻の終わりだ。\n観念するんだな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01071",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "うう……鋼のエルスと出会っちまうとは",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01072",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "さて、取り調べといこう。「ヌルスラの鷹」、\nお前、ベスティラに来た用件はなんだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01073",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そ、それは……それだけは言えねえ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01074",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "大人しく吐いたほうが楽になるぞ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01075",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あの、ボス！　この人、尾行してる時に\n王妃がわがままとかどうとか言ってました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01076",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "王妃……？　こいつも王宮絡みか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01077",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "こいつも、って言うと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01078",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "イザナを誘拐しようとしたアイス売りの女だ。\n行方を捜索したところ王妃の別荘に出入りしていてな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01079",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "しかも周辺を探ってみると、行方不明となったはずの\n獣人娘たちらしき目撃情報も出てきた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01080",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "お前に獣人娘を攫うように指示していたのは\nベスティラ王妃……違うか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01081",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……そこまでバレてちゃ隠し立てする義理もねえ。\nそうだよ、監察官殿の仰る通りさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01082",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あの王妃は若い獣人の娘が好みらしくてね。\nかわいい子を見ると自分の手元に置きたくなるんだと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01083",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それで俺に依頼してきたんだが、俺だけじゃなく\n他の奴らにも依頼してたんだろうな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01084",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "めちゃくちゃやるわね……いくら王妃様だって\n誘拐なんてしちゃダメでしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01085",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "手なずけた魔物を手駒として俺に貸してくれたり、\n相当場数を踏んでるはずだぜ、ありゃあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01086",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "一国の王妃ともなれば現場の一存だけでは\n逮捕は難しいが……見過ごすわけにはいかん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01087",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうね、王宮に行って問い詰めましょう！\n誰だろうが、私は遠慮しないわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01088",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "な、なによあなたたち！\n王様がこのことを知ったら、全員極刑よ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01089",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "その王様は今開かれている武道会の会場でしょ。\n緊急事態ってやつなのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01090",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ベスティラ王妃、略取・誘拐の件について\n「ヌルスラの鷹」から話は聞かせてもらったぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01091",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "なにそいつ、誰のこと？　私は何も知らなーい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01092",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ここに来るさなか、王宮の中で攫われた女性を\nすでに見つけているのだがな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01093",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……なーんだ、バレちゃったの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01094",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "でも、ここは私の国なのよ。\n私の好きにしていいじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01095",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ベスティラは諸島同盟に加盟している。\n王政といえど、この島の行政は同盟の法の下にもある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01096",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "同盟の法はこのような所業を許してはいない。\nあなたの好き勝手は、許されるものではない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01097",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "それに、誘拐された獣人には他の島の者もいた。\nこれは同盟の理念に反する行いだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01098",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "その権力を利用して自分の趣味嗜好のために、\n人々を誘拐する。これは、見過ごせない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01099",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "他の島からも人を攫っちゃってるし。これ、\n「島同士の争いを禁じる」ってことに反しちゃってるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01100",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "誰だ？　いや……そちらのお前は見覚えがあるな。\n確か、ブラオールの港にいた……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01101",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヤドヴィガ、それにキューン！\nやっぱり私たちを監視してたのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01102",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ヴァレリアさんたちのお知り合いですか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01103",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ベスティラ王妃は、私たちの「管理」対象となる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01104",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "な、なに、こいつは",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01105",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "べ、別に悪い暮らしとか監禁とかはしてないのよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01106",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ただ従者として身の回りの世話をしてもらうだけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01107",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "みんな等しく愛してあげてるし、不自由もさせてない。\n大体従者の囲い込みなんて友達もみんなやってて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01108",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "自分勝手な釈明と判断。「管理」の必要性が高い。\n最終審査に入る",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01109",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そんな……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01110",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "王妃様が悪いんですよ。こっちだって好きで\nやってるんじゃないのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01111",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "この国を管理だなんて、だ、旦那が黙ってないわよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "黙らせるまでのこと",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ちょ……ちょっと待ってください！\n勝手に話を進めないでください！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01112",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 49,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あなたたちが何者かは知りませんけど……\nこれは私たち監察官の仕事です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01113",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 50,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "その通りだ、タイニー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01114",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 51,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "諸島同盟の秩序を守るのは我々監察官の役目だ。\n口を挟まないでもらおうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01115",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 52,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "はっ、啖呵切られちまったねえ……なあ、ヤドヴィガ。\n確かに王妃の行動はまずいけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01116",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 53,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "まだアタシらが手を出すには早いんじゃないのかい？\nこの場は監察官に任せたほうがいいよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01117",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 54,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "すでにパルメの考えから外れているイェルカ姉上の\n言葉には従えない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01118",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 55,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "逆効果か。真面目すぎる子だ。多分ヴァレリアが\n自由な分、次のヤドヴィガはこういう性格になったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01119",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 56,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "我が主の命令を実行する。\nキューン、ベスティラ王妃を連れていき、審査にかける",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01120",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 57,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "う、うん……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01121",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]